# Copy and pricing

Source of truth: `apps/web/src/lib/pricing/constants.ts`.

- **Standard**: $29/month, $278/year (20% off vs $348/year).
- **Pro**: $47/month, $451/year (20% off vs $564/year).
- **Plan name**: Use **Standard** (not Starter) in user-facing copy.
- **No em dashes or en dashes**: Do not use "—" (U+2014) or "–" (U+2013). Use commas, colons, or " to " for ranges instead.
